{"word":"οἰκοδομή","slug":"οἰκοδομή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>οἰϰοδομή, ῆς, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οἰκοδόμος\">οἰκοδόμος</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘structured entity’, <b>building, structure<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in central sense<b> <a href='B:470 24:1'>Mt 24:1</a>; <a href='B:480 13:1'>Mk 13:1f</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in imagery<b> <a href='B:530 3:9'>1 Cor 3:9</a>; <a href='B:540 5:1'>2 Cor 5:1</a>; <a href='B:560 2:21'>Eph 2:21</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘strengthening of a structure’, <b>building up,</b> in imagery of inward growth <b><a href='B:520 14:19'>Ro 14:19</a>; <a href='B:520 15:2'>15:2</a>; <a href='B:530 14:3'>1 Cor 14:3</a>, <a href='B:530 14:12'>12</a>, <a href='B:530 14:26'>26</a>; <a href='B:540 10:8'>2 Cor 10:8</a>; <a href='B:540 12:19'>12:19</a>; <a href='B:540 13:10'>13:10</a>; <a href='B:560 4:12'>Eph 4:12</a>, <a href='B:560 4:16'>16</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:οἰκοδομέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:οἰκοδομία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}